Odaily Planet Daily News: Musk previously initiated a discussion in the community on optimizing the X comment algorithm. CZ responded and made four suggestions: 
1. Prohibit automatic robot replies, or allow authors to limit replies and prohibit the use of robots; 
2. Support sorting comments by the number of account followers, account registration time, etc. (prioritize replies from accounts with longer follow time); 
3. Support sorting comments by "people I follow"; 
4. Remember the last sorting preference.
